<?php include_once($_SERVER['DOCUMENT_ROOT'] . '/assets/php/html/min/imports/importPath.php'); ?><!doctypehtml><html lang=en><meta charset=utf-8><?php include_once('global/sharedStyles.php'); ?><link href=/assets/styles/css/min/local/help/how-to-redeem/instructions.min.css rel=stylesheet><title>How to Redeem: Borderlands 3 - ShiftCodesTK</title><meta content="How to Redeem: BL3 - ShiftCodesTK"name=title><meta content="How to Redeem: Borderlands 3 - ShiftCodesTK"property=og:title><meta content="How to Redeem: Borderlands 3 - ShiftCodesTK"property=twitter:title><meta content="How to redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands 3"name=description><meta content="How to redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands 3"property=og:description><meta content="How to redeem SHiFT Codes in Borderlands 3"property=twitter:description><meta name=canonical href=https://shiftcodestk.com/help/how-to-redeem/bl3><meta content=https://shiftcodestk.com/how-to-redeem/bl3 property=og:url><meta content=bl3_3 name=header:image><meta content=https://shiftcodestk.com/assets/img/metadata/bl3/3.png property=og:image><meta content=https://shiftcodestk.com/assets/img/metadata/bl3/3.png property=twitter:image><link href=/assets/manifests/bl3.webmanifest rel=manifest><meta content=#ffb600 name=theme-color-tm id=theme_color_tm><?php include_once('global/head.php'); ?><body data-theme=bl3><?php include_once('global/beforeContent.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/main-header.php'); ?><main class=content-wrapper><?php include_once('local/how-to-redeem-instructions.php'); ?></main><div class=setup><div class="step 1">Either by heading to the <strong>Main Menu</strong>, or by opening the <strong>Start Menu</strong> in-game, navigate to the <em>Social</em> menu.</div><div class="step 2">Switch to the <strong>SHiFT</strong> tab.</div><div class="step 3">If you have not already registered and signed in to <strong>SHiFT</strong>, you will be prompted to do so.</div><div class="step 4">Enter the 25-character SHiFT Code into the provided fields. Once you are finished, click <em>Submit</em>.</div><div class="step 5">If successful, you will receive a confirmation message. The reward from the SHiFT Code will also appear in the <strong>Rewards History</strong> section.</div><div class="step 6">If you are not already in-game, load into any character and return to the <strong>Social</strong> menu. Then, switch to the <strong>Mail</strong> tab. Select the <strong>rewards</strong> from your mailbox to claim them.</div><div class="step 7">You can now make your way to the <strong>Golden Chest</strong> aboard <strong>Sanctuary</strong> to spend your Golden Keys. The Golden Chest can be found near in the hallway leading to <strong>Marcus Munitions</strong>. Opening the chest will cost <strong>one Golden Key</strong>, and the rewards will be droppped at the <strong>level of your current character</strong>, regardless of playthrough.</div></div><?php include_once('local/support-footer.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/afterContent.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/sharedScripts.php'); ?><script async src="/assets/scripts/min/local/help/how-to-redeem/instructions.min.js?v=<?php echo $svQueryString; ?>"></script>